Name: Minnesota Tribe
Details: One of the Second Succession War unsolved mysteries, at the beginning of the was there were rumores of a mysterious Deep Periphery group that had appeared in in a series of raids against border worlds of the Draconis Combine. Rumored to be a part of the army that followed General Kerensky into the Exodus, the raiders jumped back to the Periphery after raiding a number of worlds and were never seen again.
